<h1> Review an article: </h1>
 
<p style = "font-family: didot">
 
<form action="/reviews" method="post">
Pick an article: <br> <br> <% @articles.each do |article| %>
    <input type="radio" name="user[article_id][]" value="<%= article.id %>" id="<%= article.id %>"> <%= "\"#{article.title}\" by #{article.author}" %> <br> <br>
<% end %>
 
Write a review: <br> <br> <input type="text" name="user[review]">
 
<br> <br> <br>
<input type="submit" name="submit" id="submit" value="Submit">
</form>
</p> 